description: Hono.js best pactices  for building APIs and middleware
globs: apps/engine/**/*.(ts|tsx)
---
- Use middleware for authentication and logging
- Implement route handlers using `app.get`, `app.post`, etc.
- Utilize `c.env`  for environment variables in Cloudfare Workers
- Structure routes modularly for maintainability
- Handle errors globally with `app.onError`
- Use `c.text()`, `c.json()`, and `c.redirect()` for response handling
- Leverage caching with `Cache-Control` or KV storage